          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <actionDate>2013-03-20</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Justice Safety Valve Act of 2013 - Amends the federal criminal code to authorize a federal court to impose a sentence below a statutory minimum if necessary to avoid violating federal provisions prescribing factors courts must consider in imposing a sentence. Requires the court to give the parties notice of its intent to impose a lower sentence and to state in writing the factors requiring such a sentence. </p>]]></text>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
